criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients undergoing uniport VATS for left / right upper lobectomy in Shanghai
             Pulmonary Hospital

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  preoperative presence of any unstable systemic disease, such as active infection,
             uncontrolled hypertension, or unstable angina pectoris;

          -  previous ipsilateral thoracic surgery;

          -  preoperative X-ray findings of pneumonia or atelectasis;

          -  bleeding tendency;

          -  anticoagulant use;

          -  pregnancy or breastfeeding;

          -  converted to open chest;

          -  the patient underwent pneumonectomy or segmental resection or wedge resection;

          -  severe adhesion occurred during the operation
